---
title: Sheet Pan Chicken Fajitas with Peppers and Feta
description: Sizzling fajitas make everyone else in the restaurant wish they had ordered them too! We've converted this festive favourite into a simple sheet pan supper at home. Quick, easy and full of flavour!
